data.description: Are you ready to call this 3 bedroom, 2 bath 1,790 sq ft home in South West Visalia, Ca. ''Home'' ? Interior updates include white cabinets with full extension drawers, Grey Quartz counters with white subway tile plus stainless steel appliances and newer Goodman HVAC unit. Enjoy wood look vinyl plan flooring throughout with carpet in the bedrooms and large loft area. There is wood panel accents on the living room fireplace wall, Vaulted ceilings and lots of windows for natural lighting.  Upstairs is a large area for a game room, pool table or office. There is a mini sink with cabinets and counter for entertaining as well. The garage features a drive through door for convenient access to the back yard. Outdoors is a spacious yard area with playset and gated mini yard towards the West side. Don't wait, call to see this home today.
